Initialise Anaconda: (conda)
	$ source /home/up2/anaconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh



Initialise OpenVino:
	$ source /opt/intel/openvino_2019.1.133/bin/setupvars.sh



Start Intel studio:
	$ sudo /opt/intel/system_studio_2019/iss_ide_eclipse-launcher.sh



To start Face detect solution Solution 
	$ conda source activate faceDetect



Make new Work environment:
	$ conda env create -f faceDetect_env.yml

Activate work environment:
source activate env_name



***********************
conda envs:  (list all: $ conda env list)

faceDetect     : normal build	(main working)
opencv_test    : normal build 	(backup build)
opencv_test_pr : opencv extra build (extra functions opencv)




Logitech camera Control Package:
	$ sudo apt-get install v4l-utils

$ v4l2-ctl -d /dev/video0 --set-ctrl=focus_absolute=0
$ v4l2-ctl -d /dev/video0 --set-ctrl=sharpness=200
$ v4l2-ctl -d /dev/video0 --set-ctrl=zoom_absolute=0 

